<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 16:07:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>本-格维尔和他的妻子吹嘘武装犹太以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</link><description>上周，以色列议会国家安全委员会批准了国家安全部长本-格维尔提出的枪支许可证规定修正案，以便在南部战事持续不断的情况下，获得许可证的条件更加宽松</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 15:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>150,000 枚火箭和导弹：以色列在与真主党的战争中将遭遇的武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</link><description>根据最新的已知评估，真主党拥有数万枚远程导弹、广泛的防空系统和突击队</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 15:33:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级官员警告以色列-加沙战争中中东局势升级的可能性增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀和国务卿安东尼·布林肯认为“局势可能会大幅升级”，担心真主党和伊朗可能与以色列发生直接冲突</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 14:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争的斗争正在华盛顿升温</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-battle-over-the-israel-hamas-war-is-heating-up-in-washington/0000018b-5735-d2b2-addf-777d25eb0000</link><description>尽管美国总统乔·拜登表示他全力支持以色列，但其官员的行动却描绘出一幅略有不同的景象。华盛顿特区的民主党和共和党内部也出现了第二条战线</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 14:40:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-battle-over-the-israel-hamas-war-is-heating-up-in-washington/0000018b-5735-d2b2-addf-777d25eb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯、真主党和胡塞武装：伊朗如何卷入以色列-哈马斯战争？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/hamas-hezbollah-and-the-houthis-what-is-irans-involvement-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-4318-d242-abef-533e2d6a0000</link><description>虽然只有一份报告明确将伊朗与 10 月 7 日以色列南部的暴行联系起来，但人们的共识是，伊朗一直在操纵其在加沙、约旦河西岸、黎巴嫩甚至也门的恐怖组织代理人。然后是以色列与沙特阿拉伯关系正常化的小问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 13:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/hamas-hezbollah-and-the-houthis-what-is-irans-involvement-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-4318-d242-abef-533e2d6a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对以色列的生存构成生存威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-is-an-existential-threat-to-israels-survival/0000018b-5733-d8e2-a1eb-f737a78b0000</link><description>以色列在国内和国际上的脆弱是伊朗及其代理人以及该国失败的领导人内塔尼亚胡的过错。美国和德国正在提供前所未有的军事、道义和外交支持，以支撑以色列公众，同时也防止加沙地带出现天文数字般的死亡人数</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 12:44:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-is-an-existential-threat-to-israels-survival/0000018b-5733-d8e2-a1eb-f737a78b0000</guid></item><item><title>让女性应对以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/women-prove-they-wouldve-handled-israel-hamas-war-better/0000018b-5738-d8e2-a1eb-f73ead300000</link><description>面对以色列与加沙战争期间男性领导力的失败，一些女性因她们的勇敢而闪耀并鼓舞人心 ■ 可惜她们被排除在决策之外</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 12:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/women-prove-they-wouldve-handled-israel-hamas-war-better/0000018b-5738-d8e2-a1eb-f73ead300000</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰综合症：为什么西方领导人无法停止访问战时以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-ukraine-syndrome-why-western-leaders-cant-stop-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-569b-dc3c-a5df-debb06080000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理可能会很感激有机会会见那些没有指责他破坏自己国家的人，但拜登、马克龙和他的同事们的访问有真正的地缘政治原因。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 11:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-ukraine-syndrome-why-western-leaders-cant-stop-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-569b-dc3c-a5df-debb06080000</guid></item><item><title>“我们等待他们平安无事的消息。它从未来过&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-waited-for-a-message-that-yarden-kinneret-and-carmel-were-okay-but-it-never-came/0000018b-568e-df6e-a5db-76ee061b0000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特别项目 ■ Roni Roman 想象她的姐姐 Yarden 帮助被囚禁的伤员。她的哥哥强迫军队寻找她。他们一起试图了解亚登和她的搭档阿隆的妹妹发生了什么事</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 10:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-waited-for-a-message-that-yarden-kinneret-and-carmel-were-okay-but-it-never-came/0000018b-568e-df6e-a5db-76ee061b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列自2000年代以来首次使用战机袭击约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-uses-warplane-to-strike-in-west-bank-for-first-time-since-2000s/0000018b-56c3-d02b-a3db-ffdf22400000</link><description>以色列军方表示，杰宁难民营的空袭目标是一个计划重复边境社区大屠杀的恐怖分子。 巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来，已有 90 名巴勒斯坦人被以色列的炮火杀害。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 10:11:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-uses-warplane-to-strike-in-west-bank-for-first-time-since-2000s/0000018b-56c3-d02b-a3db-ffdf22400000</guid></item><item><title>反犹太主义暴露，法国左翼与哈马斯一起自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-french-left-is-commiting-suicide-along-with-hamas/0000018b-569f-d1d7-ab8b-7edfecb80000</link><description>拒绝谴责哈马斯的残酷杀戮是恐怖行为不仅是反犹太主义，而且为极右翼掌权铺平了道路</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-french-left-is-commiting-suicide-along-with-hamas/0000018b-569f-d1d7-ab8b-7edfecb80000</guid></item><item><title>国防部消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡发起运动，指责以色列军方未能预测哈马斯袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-on-campaign-to-blame-idf-for-failure-to-predict-attack-defense-sources-say/0000018b-5688-d5d2-afef-d6fde37a0000</link><description>以色列总理任命了一名新发言人与军事记者联络，这是一个不寻常的举动，一位消息人士称，他们听说他诽谤军官</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:28:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-on-campaign-to-blame-idf-for-failure-to-predict-attack-defense-sources-say/0000018b-5688-d5d2-afef-d6fde37a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对以色列造成了大屠杀。他早就该辞职了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-strategy-to-cling-to-power-wont-save-him-from-an-enduring-legacy-of-failure/0000018b-5640-d5d2-afef-d6fd6ccf0000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡现在指望疲劳和公众的绝望来帮助他保住职位，但不能相信他能够管理一场战争，这也无法让他摆脱持久的失败遗产。当战争结束时，无论是三周还是三个月，所有的政治地狱都会解脱</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-strategy-to-cling-to-power-wont-save-him-from-an-enduring-legacy-of-failure/0000018b-5640-d5d2-afef-d6fd6ccf0000</guid></item><item><title>美军在动荡的中东面临日益严重的威胁，击落导弹和无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/u-s-military-shoots-down-missiles-drones-as-it-faces-growing-threats-in-middle-east/0000018b-5673-dc3c-a5df-defb8e870000</link><description>在多起独立事件中——来自也门的导弹、来自伊拉克和叙利亚的无人机——美军被迫在中东各地采取行动，试图缓和并防止更广泛的冲突</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:03:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/u-s-military-shoots-down-missiles-drones-as-it-faces-growing-threats-in-middle-east/0000018b-5673-dc3c-a5df-defb8e870000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的人质特使危及所有被哈马斯绑架的人的生命</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-hostage-envoy-endangers-the-lives-of-all-those-kidnapped-by-hamas/0000018b-538a-df6e-a5db-77eec70e0000</link><description>被任命负责确保加沙人质获释的退休准将盖尔·赫希（Gal Hirsch）是一位“自大狂的救世主”和核心圈子比比主义者，他更关心自己的政治生涯，而不是他所承担的微妙工作； “把他的自我带到桌面上，而不是其他”</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 08:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-hostage-envoy-endangers-the-lives-of-all-those-kidnapped-by-hamas/0000018b-538a-df6e-a5db-77eec70e0000</guid></item><item><title>在土耳其，哈马斯的袭击引发了以色列仇恨和彻底反犹太主义的海啸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-turkey-hamas-attacks-trigger-tsunami-of-israel-hate-and-outright-antisemitism/0000018b-5342-dc3c-a5df-dfea36ed0000</link><description>没有人预料到埃尔多安领导下的土耳其会过度声援哈马斯暴行的受害者。但跨党派对以色列“野蛮行径”的大量谴责、内塔尼亚胡和希特勒之间的比较以及对哈马斯的拥抱远远超出了未能向以色列受害者表示任何哀悼的程度</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 08:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/in-turkey-hamas-attacks-trigger-tsunami-of-israel-hate-and-outright-antisemitism/0000018b-5342-dc3c-a5df-dfea36ed0000</guid></item><item><title>法国和加拿大情报机构称，造成加沙医院爆炸的是巴勒斯坦火箭弹，而不是以色列空袭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/french-canadian-intelligence-say-palestinian-rocket-caused-gaza-hospital-blast/0000018b-560f-dc3c-a5df-deafdee30000</link><description>法国情报官员表示，哈马斯武器库中的几枚火箭弹携带的炸药重量与此相当，其中包括一枚伊朗制造的火箭和一枚巴勒斯坦制造的火箭。法国官员补充说，他们的情报均未表明以色列发动了袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 07:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/french-canadian-intelligence-say-palestinian-rocket-caused-gaza-hospital-blast/0000018b-560f-dc3c-a5df-deafdee30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队与真主党交火，哈马斯火箭弹炸伤以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-live/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-fire-in-northern-border-idf-gears-up-for-gaza-ground-invasion/0000018b-554b-d5d2-afef-d5ff03e00000</link><description>以色列军队对从黎巴嫩边境逼近的恐怖分子嫌疑人进行空袭 ■ 自第二次起义以来，以色列国防军首次在约旦河西岸使用战斗机 ■ 靠近黎巴嫩边境的另外 14 个以色列城镇将被疏散 ■ 意大利总理、塞浦路斯总统对以色列进行短暂访问 ■自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 人被哈马斯杀害 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：4,137 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，13,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 04:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-live/israel-and-hezbollah-trade-fire-in-northern-border-idf-gears-up-for-gaza-ground-invasion/0000018b-554b-d5d2-afef-d5ff03e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵报告称，在以色列国防军内获得精神支持的机会有限，寻求平民治疗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-report-limited-access-to-mental-support-in-idf-seek-civilian-treatment/0000018b-539d-d1d7-ab8b-7fdfb8b80000</link><description>一位创伤专家表示，以色列军队没有采取积极措施来预防创伤，只是等待士兵寻求帮助。专业人士警告说，如果不采取积极措施为他们提供情感支持，许多以色列士兵将很难重返岗位。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 03:42:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-report-limited-access-to-mental-support-in-idf-seek-civilian-treatment/0000018b-539d-d1d7-ab8b-7fdfb8b80000</guid></item><item><title>底特律犹太教堂主席被发现在家外被刺死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/detroit-synagogue-president-found-stabbed-to-death-outside-her-home/0000018b-553c-df6e-a5db-757e496f0000</link><description>40 岁的萨曼莎·沃尔 (Samantha Woll) 是底特律的一位民主党活动家和著名的犹太教非宗教领袖，她在家外被刺死。犹太社区消息人士称，他们没有任何信息表明这是一起与以色列对哈马斯战争引发的紧张局势有关的仇恨犯罪</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 02:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/detroit-synagogue-president-found-stabbed-to-death-outside-her-home/0000018b-553c-df6e-a5db-757e496f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>